The department coordinates with FEU Cso offices to cascade needed information to the student body. Additionally, the department formulates survey questions, and gathers data, which are rooted from collective student grievances. The department further conducts comprehensive research and produces information regarding these concerns. Moreover, the department crafts petitions, request letters, and clarificatory letters to address students' concerns and grievances. summarize and make it concise."

message.text:
Sabi nga ni Ariana Grande, “𝘐'𝘭𝘭 𝘨𝘪𝘷𝘦 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘐 𝘩𝘢𝘷𝘦 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘯𝘰𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘭𝘦𝘴𝘴, 𝘐 𝘱𝘳𝘰𝘮𝘪𝘴𝘦,” which is what we exactly do here in this department dahil LAHAT gagawin namin para lang sa Students’ Welfare and Grievances (SWAG) 🤕🤍

Before the enrollment period palang, the department is already creating letters after letters on top of the 1st Semester Enrollment Helpdesk tulad nalang ng:

✅Recommendation for Blended Learning Modality
✅Petition for Transporation Assistance (for Batch 2025 Graduated)
✅Recommendation to Shift to Asynchronous Classes 

Kaya ano pa ang hinihintay mo? tARIANA sa SWAG! 🧚🏻‍♀️ We don't want to be your, "𝘛𝘩𝘢𝘯𝘬 𝘺𝘰𝘶, 𝘯𝘦𝘹𝘵," dahil nag-aabang na sa'yo ang SWAGrandeng mga pasabog! 🤩

SWAG is happy to welcome new members that can help in furthering the student body’s best interests, kaya join na! 🫵🏼

JOIN FEUCSO SWAG HERE: ⬇️
https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

#fyp #arianagrande #myeverything  #viral

media.accessibility_caption: May be an image of text that says "OFFICE OF THE PRESIDENT STUDENTS' WELFARE AND GRIEVANCEST The Students' Welfare and Grievances (SWAG) responds to students' concerns, inquiries, and grievances. The department coordinates with FEU Cso offices to cascade needed information to the student body. Additionally, the department formulates survey questions, and gathers data, which are rooted from collective student grievances. The department further conducts comprehensive research and produces information regarding these concerns. Moreover, the department crafts petitions, request letters, and clarificatory letters to address students' concerns and grievances. summarize and make it concise."

message.text:
Sabi nga ni Ariana Grande, “𝘐'𝘭𝘭 𝘨𝘪𝘷𝘦 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘐 𝘩𝘢𝘷𝘦 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘯𝘰𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘭𝘦𝘴𝘴, 𝘐 𝘱𝘳𝘰𝘮𝘪𝘴𝘦,” which is what we exactly do here in this department dahil LAHAT gagawin namin para lang sa Students’ Welfare and Grievances (SWAG) 🤕🤍

Before the enrollment period palang, the department is already creating letters after letters on top of the 1st Semester Enrollment Helpdesk tulad nalang ng:

✅Recommendation for Blended Learning Modality
✅Petition for Transporation Assistance (for Batch 2025 Graduated)
✅Recommendation to Shift to Asynchronous Classes 

Kaya ano pa ang hinihintay mo? tARIANA sa SWAG! 🧚🏻‍♀️ We don't want to be your, "𝘛𝘩𝘢𝘯𝘬 𝘺𝘰𝘶, 𝘯𝘦𝘹𝘵," dahil nag-aabang na sa'yo ang SWAGrandeng mga pasabog! 🤩

SWAG is happy to welcome new members that can help in furthering the student body’s best interests, kaya join na! 🫵🏼

JOIN FEUCSO SWAG HERE: ⬇️
https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

#fyp #arianagrande #myeverything  #viral

cc: Raezon Gonzales Shanaia Kaye Shanella Ison Andrea Lim
